DESCRIPTION: Command to run TSLint and Prettier linters on the pdf-lib codebase to maintain code style and formatting standards.
SOURCE: https://github.com/Hopding/pdf-lib/blob/master/docs/CONTRIBUTING.md#2025-04-12_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
yarn lint
```

